+/**
+ * A basic Wallet to exercise various OID4VCI message flows.
+ *
+ * Wallet state between messages is maintained in {@code OID4VCTestContext}.
+ *
+ * @author <a href="mailto:tdiesler@ibm.com">Thomas Diesler</a>
